theme = ExtResource("9_doa4r")
text = "Press the R key to manually reroll the entity properties.

This here, is a showcase of the E.N.T.I.T.Y system. All objects (well, almost) are technically THE SAME object, but
with 600+ behaviors (about 300 being quite minor though) being able to be adjusted from the base state. This here, is an extreme example, made to show
that none of these properties negate any of the others. There will be an ENTITY EDITOR at some point, but for now if you wish to create
your own entities, just copy any already existing entity scene, and adjust its properties (on the right of the screen) within the godot editor."

